In Fukushima, some people seem to forget that the accident was due to two natural disasters of an unprecedented scale, which resulted in the deaths of tens of thousands of people.
The nuclear sector will learn from this accident, as it did from the previous two.
Thanks to these advances and cooperation between the security authorities, and French and German operators and builders, the EPR presents a design capable of resisting such phenomena.
